The paper proposes a sampling-based training framework for semi-supervised graph embedding methods to achieve better performance with smaller training data set. This involves integrating sampling theory and embedding methods in a pipeline form. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the following arXiv CS sub-categories: 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning)
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks)
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence)
- cs.CL (Computation and Language)
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition)
